natural_language: The system will install updates, but only if there is enough disk space and the update is available.
The application will launch, but not if the operating system is outdated or the user is not logged in.
The feature will be enabled, but only when the user is authenticated and the feature is available.
The service will start automatically, but not if manual mode is selected or the service is not configured.
The device will enter sleep mode, but only after 5 minutes of inactivity and when the device is idle.
Notifications will appear, but not when do not disturb mode is active or when the phone is switched off.
llm_output: NOT (NOT DOOR_OPEN OR NOT POWER_ON) IMPLIES NOTIFICATIONS_APPEAR

natural_language: The backup will proceed, but only if the storage device is connected and backup is enabled.
The system will reboot, but not if critical processes are running or reboot is not requested.
The settings will be saved, but only when the form is validated and the user has confirmed.
The connection will be established, but not without network availability.
